      <title>卢拉将任命前财务总监曼特加为布拉斯科董事会成员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/lula-will-name-former-finance-chief-mantega-to-braskem-board</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情人士透露，巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦预计将任命前财政部长吉多·曼特加为 Braskem SA 董事会成员，因为政府力争在企业决策中发挥更大影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/lula-will-name-former-finance-chief-mantega-to-braskem-board</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 14:03:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Starmer Deepfake 与 X 之战凸显英国大选担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/battle-with-x-over-starmer-deepfake-highlights-uk-election-worry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[社交媒体公司 X 拒绝删除英国反对党领袖凯尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 的深度造假音频片段，这在工党内部敲响了警钟，提醒人们警惕大选前虚假信息的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/battle-with-x-over-starmer-deepfake-highlights-uk-election-worry</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰考虑征召囚犯补充饱受战争摧残的军队</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/ukraine-mulls-drafting-convicts-to-replenish-war-battered-troops</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰立法者计划考虑一项允许监狱囚犯加入战争的法案，在俄罗斯最近取得进展后，该国正在寻求加强前线人力的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/ukraine-mulls-drafting-convicts-to-replenish-war-battered-troops</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 13:31:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孤立的欧尔班寻求“占领”欧盟作为极右势力浪潮的一部分</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/isolated-orban-seeks-to-occupy-eu-as-part-of-far-right-surge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理维克多·欧尔班誓言要“占领”欧盟，作为他预计今年欧盟范围内选举中极右翼势力激增的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/isolated-orban-seeks-to-occupy-eu-as-part-of-far-right-surge</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 13:20:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟与埃及将加强关系作为投资计划的一部分</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/eu-egypt-to-strengthen-relationship-as-part-of-investment-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟准备将其与埃及的关系升级为“战略伙伴关系”，此举可能会为这个北非国家带来数十亿欧元的资金和投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/eu-egypt-to-strengthen-relationship-as-part-of-investment-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 13:16:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法官裁定，如果首席检察官离职，威利斯可以继续审理特朗普佐治亚州案件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/trump-prosecutor-fani-willis-can-stay-on-georgia-election-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法官裁定，只要与富尔顿县地方检察官法妮·威利斯有恋爱关系的首席检察官内森·韦德下台，富尔顿县地方检察官法妮·威利斯就可以继续监督佐治亚州唐纳德·特朗普的选举干预案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/trump-prosecutor-fani-willis-can-stay-on-georgia-election-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 13:08:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塞内加尔最高法院驳回反对派推迟选举的提议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/senegal-supreme-court-rejects-opposition-bid-to-delay-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞内加尔最高法院在预定投票前 10 天驳回了反对派政治家卡里姆·韦德 (Karim Wade) 取消总统选举的请求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/senegal-supreme-court-rejects-opposition-bid-to-delay-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 13:07:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列批准拉法在地面行动前“撤离”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/israel-prepares-rafah-evacuation-after-netanyahu-approves-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡办公室称，以色列正准备在计划对巴勒斯坦飞地采取地面行动之前将加沙拉法的平民转移。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/israel-prepares-rafah-evacuation-after-netanyahu-approves-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 12:57:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>米莱法令在参议院被废除后遭遇重大挫折</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/milei-s-bold-decree-suffers-major-setback-after-repeal-in-senate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷参议院周四以 42 比 25 的投票结果否决了总统哈维尔·米莱 (Javier Milei) 的全面行政命令，他最初的休克疗法正处于崩溃的边缘。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/milei-s-bold-decree-suffers-major-setback-after-repeal-in-senate</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 23:00:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管有限制，中国仍将投资加拿大矿业：特使</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/china-to-invest-in-canada-mining-despite-crackdown-envoy-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国大使表示，尽管加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多“不幸”地打压外国投资，但中国将继续在加拿大国内关键矿产行业开展业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/china-to-invest-in-canada-mining-despite-crackdown-envoy-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 15:31:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
